{"tid":2126610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港府防疫料「加辣」 擬禁午市堂食","createTime":"2020-07-27T02:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T03:06:37.000Z","uid":363119,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"27ebaa1669960a16eef42751549fbe973fe9ca04","tid":2126610,"uid":363119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:54:50.000Z","msg":"強制室外戴口罩 街市超市限人流<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疫情嚴峻，據悉行政會議今日將召開特別會議，拍板防疫措施加辣，當中包括至少3招：（1）禁午市堂食；（2）強制室外亦要戴口罩，但會有一些豁免；（3）進入濕街市和超級市場的人數，將有限制。<br />\n<br />\n行會今開特別會議<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://paper.hket.com/article/2706424/%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%E6%96%99%E3%80%8C%E5%8A%A0%E8%BE%A3%E3%80%8D%20%E6%93%AC%E7%A6%81%E5%8D%88%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%82%E9%A3%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpaper.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2706424%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2596%2599%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%25BE%25A3%25E3%2580%258D%2520%25E6%2593%25AC%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%258D%2588%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%2582%25E9%25A3%259F&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qx%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=2dbe765b\" target=\"_blank\">https://paper.hket.com/article/2706424/%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%E6%96%99%E3%80%8C%E5%8A%A0%E8%BE%A3%E3%80%8D%20%E6%93%AC%E7%A6%81%E5%8D%88%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%82%E9%A3%9F</a>"},{"pid":"483bc461aa2a88be38765262eb4ffb2de3397763","tid":2126610,"uid":62192,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:55:36.000Z","msg":"我唔食辣點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無端端加辣on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4350937b62fe8025d6eed11c8bd6cdf958cc8d43","tid":2126610,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"483bc461aa2a88be38765262eb4ffb2de3397763","tid":2126610,"uid":62192,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:55:36.000Z","msg":"我唔食辣點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無端端加辣